==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foreignness
<hw>For"eign*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being foreign;
remoteness; want of relation or appropriateness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let not the <qex>foreignness</qex> of the subject hinder you from
endeavoring to set me right.</q> <rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>foreignness</qex> of complexion.</q> <rj><qau>G.
Eliot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forein</ent>⟦br⟧
